+	 method_steps:{zh:"<ol><li>加密取最近 60 根 4 小时 K(约 10 天),美股/ETF 取最近 40 个交易日。</li><li>对收盘价取对数并在每个窗口内 z 标准化,去掉价格量级,只比较形状。</li><li>候选窗口必须在当前窗口之前结束,且后续完整覆盖最长前瞻期,避免未来函数。</li><li>corr 按皮尔逊相关排序;DTW 先由 corr 预筛 400 段,再以 Sakoe–Chiba 带宽约窗口的 1/6 重排。相邻案例至少间隔半个窗口,减少重复。</li><li>取加密 Top 50、股票/ETF Top 40 案例,统计后续上涨比例、中位收益与 25–75% 分位;baseline 使用所有合格历史时点。</li><li>加密季节性 7/30/90 天分别换算为 42/180/540 根 4 小时 K;股票/ETF 使用 5/21/63 个交易日。图中路径和收益均为历史样本统计,不是模型目标价。</li></ol>",en:"<ol><li>Crypto uses the latest 60 four-hour bars (~10 days); stocks/ETFs use 40 trading days.</li><li>Log closes are z-scored within each window, removing price level so only shape is compared.</li><li>Candidate windows must end before the current window and retain a fully observed longest horizon, preventing look-ahead.</li><li>corr ranks Pearson correlation. DTW reranks a 400-window corr prefilter with a Sakoe–Chiba band of about one-sixth of the window. Analogs are separated by at least half a window to reduce duplicates.</li><li>Top 50 crypto or Top 40 stock/ETF analogs produce up-rate, median and 25–75% returns; baseline uses all eligible dates.</li><li>Crypto seasonality converts 7/30/90 calendar days to 42/180/540 four-hour bars; stocks/ETFs use 5/21/63 trading days. Paths and returns are historical sample summaries, not model targets.</li></ol>"},
